Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:10.70,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.03,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.31,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.37,0:00:37.77,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and the others finally \Narrived at the Underwater Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:39.06,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But once they got there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.39,0:00:42.80,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are after the \Nmagic stone, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.80,0:00:46.25,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,If you want it, why don't \Nwe play a little game?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:48.65,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,...a mysterious old man called the high priest
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:51.48,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and nine temple mages were waiting for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.48,0:00:54.90,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The high priest told Asta and the other \NBlack Bulls, who were separated,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:00:58.53,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,that if they wanted the magic stone, they\Nmust battle the temple mages, nine-on-nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.86,0:01:01.85,italics,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Victory goes to the first team \Nto wipe out the other team,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.85,0:01:05.53,italics,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,or whichever team has the \Nmost members left in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.53,0:01:07.39,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! This is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.39,0:01:09.71,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,A blood-soaked battle! I'm super pumped!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.71,0:01:11.48,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Nine?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.48,0:01:15.01,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,There should be ten of us...\NWe're missing one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:17.10,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's so easy to understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:19.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.43,0:01:21.49,main,Octopus mage,0000,0000,0000,,That's funny...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.49,0:01:24.68,main,Octopus mage,0000,0000,0000,,I can't seem to sense any magic from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.73,0:01:28.98,main,Octopus mage,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I picked a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.49,0:01:33.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna find out if I'm \Nactually a loser or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:06.64,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,480)}Temple Battle Royale
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:12.49,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, why don't we watch from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:14.88,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,I've got plenty of food and drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:20.35,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you old geezer,\Ndon't leave me out of the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:22.64,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I got all pumped up, but now I'm sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.66,0:03:27.64,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,You're a bit too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:33.23,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,All the people outside, as well as myself,\Nare very excited for this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:36.48,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be no fun if it were to end quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:40.56,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you really do get it, gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.56,0:03:41.54,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You've got good taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:44.31,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,I do, don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:49.42,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, it looks like a few \Nmatch-ups have already begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:51.96,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,All right. If any of mine lose, I'll kill 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:57.24,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,So cold... Damn that geezer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.24,0:03:59.38,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.99,0:04:01.10,main,Seahorse mage,0000,0000,0000,,Hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:04.84,main,Seahorse mage,0000,0000,0000,,You're at a total disadvantage with \Nfire magic in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.55,main,Seahorse mage,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:13.06,main,Moray Mage,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not pick on \Nfrail-looking guys like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:16.19,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna fight me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:19.85,main,Puffer Mage,0000,0000,0000,,I know you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.85,0:04:22.12,main,Puffer mage,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Black Bulls, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:25.53,main,Puffer mage,0000,0000,0000,,You're the weakest of the Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:29.03,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie's waiting for me.\NHurry up and come at me, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:35.08,main,Octopus mage,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, it's pretty pointless \Nfor you to wave around that rusty sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.51,0:04:39.09,main,Octopus mage,0000,0000,0000,,My mollusk magic can \Nparry any kind of attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:40.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:46.20,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this exciting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:50.31,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way, what are your knights' ranks?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:52.78,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,They're all junior magic knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:55.56,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you even know \Nabout that, living down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:59.61,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,According to your ranking system,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:04.01,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,my temple mages would be more\Npowerful than intermediate knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:07.49,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Those juniors don't stand a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:09.00,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:10.66,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's not good...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:15.90,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Unless those idiots are actually \Nstronger than usual for their titles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:19.00,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:24.52,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think I'm gonna get discouraged \Njust because I'm surrounded by water.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.52,0:05:26.97,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna serve all of you up like grilled fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:29.51,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,He must've been one of the weaker ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:32.22,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,So... I wonder where \Nall the strong ones are?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:33.50,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:37.19,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I need to finish this nonsense quick\Nso I can go back to doting on Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.13,0:05:40.93,main,Octopus mage,0000,0000,0000,,This... isn't right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.93,0:05:46.15,main,Octopus mage,0000,0000,0000,,My mollusk magic should be able to \Ndeflect any kind of physical attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:49.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My sword is anti-magic! That junk won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:51.62,main,Octopus mage,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Next, next!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.86,0:06:00.82,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, you idiots! \NBeat the crap out of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:04.13,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Those fools let down their guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.44,0:06:08.07,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, gramps, I forgot! We should \Nbet on which team is gonna win!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:10.10,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I bet 10,000 yuls on the Bulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:13.01,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Grr... The battle's just begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:16.93,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,They won't be able to defeat the \Nremaining priests so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:21.52,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Especially the Three Great Priests, \Nwho are on par with senior knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.51,0:06:26.49,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Badump, badump...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.16,0:06:28.99,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Sneak, sneak, sneak, sneak...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:31.67,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Whew... Man, that was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.67,0:06:34.45,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could fight \Na guy who looks that strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:39.19,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I've been trying to get to the places I \Nmarked outside, but I can't for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:43.46,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That means I can only use my spatial \Nmagic to get to places I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.37,italics,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I forgot to mention this,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:49.53,italics,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,but you won't be able to leave my \Nplayground until the game's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:51.67,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Are you watching me, gramps?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:55.29,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Finral, why the hell are you hiding? \NHurry up and fight, or I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:56.52,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:59.59,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, are you with the old guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:02.74,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We're enjoying some food and drinks \Nwhile we watch you guys fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:07.40,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Come on, make him \Nstop this violent game!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:10.15,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What? It's fun to watch \Nbecause it's so violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:11.92,italics,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.92,0:07:13.49,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,When did you two hit it off so well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:17.69,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,It's definitely no fun if \Nyou're not gonna fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.69,0:07:19.17,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let that coward get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:21.37,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,There we go! Nuisance spell activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:24.21,italics,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Game Magic: Monster Toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.79,0:07:34.63,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:38.64,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,How entertaining! I should use more of these!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.05,0:07:40.89,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you old geezer...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:44.36,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this one next. \NThis'll probably kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:47.75,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're actually on their side?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:49.23,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Nice drawing, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.85,0:07:52.78,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then... Let's see how \Nthe others are holding up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:56.56,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard Grey turned into a crab, \Nand I don't know where he went,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:58.04,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll just have to kill him later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.47,0:08:00.86,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Is Charmy battling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:06.49,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,S-Such destructive force...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:09.80,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The Underwater Temple is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:12.01,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,And so is its seafood!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:16.35,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,S-So good! Munchy, munchy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:19.16,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,This is the best I've ever had!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:21.81,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the Underwater Temple's seafood!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.61,0:08:27.81,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I wish my meal-saving prince \Ncould have some, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:33.07,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! This entire ecosystem is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:37.82,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to eat absolutely everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:45.50,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,That one there... What exactly is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:50.08,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Heave-ho! Heave-ho! What a huge haul!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:50.88,main,Dolphin mage,0000,0000,0000,,Found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:52.42,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:56.97,main,Dolphin mage,0000,0000,0000,,My, what a cute little target. I almost \Nfeel bad that I'm going to defeat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:08:59.25,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,So you're finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.25,0:09:03.75,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,But right now, I'm overflowing \Nwith undersea mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:07.67,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,If you want me to chew you up \Nthe way I chewed up those fish,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:09.99,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:15.28,main,Dolphin mage,0000,0000,0000,,Song Magic: Mother Lullaby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:28.71,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:32.65,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Why, yes, I can still eat more...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:34.13,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,One down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.29,0:09:40.41,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, sleeping counts as a K.O.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:43.78,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like the power \Nof one of my Great Priests?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:46.44,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,She's not getting any food for a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:48.38,main,Dolphin mage,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:50.98,main,Dolphin mage,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'll see those two next.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:55.63,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,All right! My clothes are finally dry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:58.03,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Who am I gonna fight next?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:02.70,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luck. I guess you're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:05.37,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! I defeated one of \Nthe enemy guys already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:09.75,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I headed this way because I felt a \Nstrong presence over here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:14.25,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I was right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:18.59,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,All right... let's decide who \Ngets a piece of 'em firâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:21.09,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! No fair, Luck! You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:25.43,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Ya snooze, ya lose, Magna!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:31.40,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning Magic: Thunderbolt Destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:35.61,main,Shark Mage,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Sea God's Shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.29,0:10:44.83,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,It's tough! My lighting should work \Npretty well against water, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:48.55,main,Shark mage,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, aren't you lively?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:54.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are these things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:06.10,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This ki... Someone's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:14.96,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Grandpa. Do you really have \Nto hit us with your nuisance spells, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.96,0:11:17.65,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever. That was a good warm-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:18.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:21.86,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He took out something that huge?\NWho the heck is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:24.56,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:26.45,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,You're Asta, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yeah, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:33.47,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about you! You use a strange \Nsword that cancels out magic, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.47,0:11:36.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes... Wait, who'd you hear that from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:39.63,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that! Check out this dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:44.28,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The hell?! He just started dancing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:58.28,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a really cool dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.62,0:12:01.61,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think they'd like this \Ndance up on the surface, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:02.99,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Heck yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:04.41,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,The name's Kiato!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:08.36,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,My dream's to become a dancer who \Ncaptivates the whole kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.36,0:12:10.41,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He just started talking about his dream?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.85,0:12:14.04,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Although people from the Underwater Temple\Ncan go to the kingdom's beaches,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:18.74,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,we can't go to the capital. \NIt's against the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:23.43,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,But if we win this fight, Grandpa said...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:26.12,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the high priest is my grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:30.36,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, he said we could use the high\N priest's authority to go up to the surface!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.36,0:12:34.52,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make a name for myself \Nand become a super famous dancer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:36.81,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He just told me all about this huge dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:38.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:40.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This all seems pretty familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:42.56,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,So listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:46.54,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take you down \Nfor the sake of my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:47.82,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.67,0:12:56.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I have my own dream, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:57.38,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:13:02.07,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna become the strongest man \Nwho protects the Clover Kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.07,0:13:03.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:07.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So for that dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:09.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.37,0:13:11.77,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,I like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:17.31,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's bet our dreams on \Na head-to-head showdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:19.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:27.83,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What am I going to do? I haven't \Nlearned a single attack spell yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:34.65,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there! I finally found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:36.75,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shoot! I'm in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:40.33,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You want to take on \Na royal such as myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.33,0:13:43.54,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some guts! This is your \Nchance to run away if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:46.92,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,First off, I'm glad you \Ncould make it, Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:49.34,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,H-How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:52.89,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. I guess you can't \Ntell with this thing on my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:56.35,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.76,0:14:00.09,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Kahono!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:03.21,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you, Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.72,0:14:15.79,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Kahono... I had no idea you were \Nfrom the Underwater Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:19.00,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you help me learn magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.47,0:14:23.05,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,I was actually looking for people who \Nwanted to come to the Underwater Temple
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:26.05,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,while I practiced singing on that beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:30.64,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,You see, when we have guests, Grandpa...\NI mean, the high priest, always holds games.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.33,0:14:33.16,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,If I win, I'll be able to go to the surface
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:35.89,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,and make my dream to \Nbecome an idol come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:39.60,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Your dream? Then you used me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:41.94,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:45.87,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I wanted to help you, \Nsince you were working so hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.87,0:14:49.10,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,and it's also true that I wanted \Nto become friends with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.10,0:14:54.24,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,But from now on, we'll fight fair and \Nsquare as opponents in this game!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:57.83,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,No! We're supposed to be friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:14:58.95,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.95,0:15:01.80,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Friends are people who can clash over \Nthings that are precious to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:04.34,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,but keep smiling together even then!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:07.84,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Song Magic: Mother Lullaby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.15,0:15:14.21,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What is this spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.21,0:15:16.01,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's going to make me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:20.77,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Sea Dragon's Lair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.64,0:15:23.31,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're ready to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.37,0:15:28.03,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Song Magic: Destructive Beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:33.64,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now, Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:35.66,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never win if you just keep defending!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:38.66,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.59,0:15:42.66,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,She only let off some magic \Nenergy, but look at that force!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.66,0:15:43.82,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:47.38,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What're you doing, Noelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:50.02,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,An attack like that won't \Nhave any effect on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.02,0:15:52.76,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Aim straight! That sucked!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.86,0:15:56.01,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:16:00.57,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't control my magic \Nwhen I'm attacking, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:04.35,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it. You're already \Ncontrolling your magic, Noelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:05.31,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:08.86,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,You're subconsciously trying \Nnot to attack people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:10.94,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,You must not want to hurt anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:14.07,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,But are you sure you're okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:16.58,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come here, Noelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:19.83,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you come here to \Nmake something come true?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:28.17,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't fight for it and win it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:29.84,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,you'll never get what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:34.59,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I... want to be useful to everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:39.35,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:52.53,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's really strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:55.32,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And what's with his moves?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:17:00.12,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's like his mind's gone somewhere else.\N It's really hard to read his ki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:09.09,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I think he's even throwing off my senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.41,0:17:11.46,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Is this his magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:13.17,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:14.93,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going up against a real sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:17.97,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,your anti-magic sword is nothing \Nmore than a lump of iron!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:22.97,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,And if I add in my dance magic,\Nyou won't be able to follow my moves!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.95,0:17:27.48,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like my grandson? Isn't he strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.95,0:17:30.30,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the kid definitely \Nknows how to handle a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:31.23,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:34.82,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now! Just surrender already, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:38.20,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good! I'm about to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:40.58,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He really is like water. \NThere's no way to catch him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:44.88,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, maybe brute strength \Nisn't the way to go here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:48.82,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I probably shouldn't try to capture water,\Nsince it has no distinct shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:53.45,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I need to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.45,0:17:54.34,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:17:59.91,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I will also become like water!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.42,0:18:02.86,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Monkeying around won't get you anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:05.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sell a monkey short!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:06.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't use magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:08.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:10.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll recreate magic with my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:14.69,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty sure there are limits \Nwhen you can't use magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:16.01,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:17.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:19.54,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use this chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:23.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,to go beyond my limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:26.66,italics,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... Just how athletic is this kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:32.75,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,My idiot's ability to pick \Nthings up quick is even greater!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:43.34,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What a rude man... Trying to set up a sneaky \Ntrap for a defenseless woman like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:48.64,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You can't really complain if you \Nfall for a trap yourself, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:56.04,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? Vanessa's usually drunk and \Nuseless before she gets warmed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:59.07,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We're in top shape today.\N I should've bet more, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:03.48,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,These guys aren't junior mages at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.48,0:19:06.64,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,But man, that lady's got some nice boobies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:09.41,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, old man. Could you get \Nthat magic stone ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:13.97,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,A really dangerous lot called the \NEye of the Midnight Sun is after that stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:16.67,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be in your best interests \Nto just hand it over to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:20.78,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,The best part of a game \Nis turning the tables.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:23.77,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get lamer than bluffing, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.77,0:19:25.74,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not bluffing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:30.55,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,If my son and grandkids get serious, \Nwe'll turn things around in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.55,0:19:35.32,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,My son is the strongest mage \Nof the Underwater Temple!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:42.15,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh... I think you're getting tired, Magna.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.15,0:19:43.57,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,You can take a little break.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:46.50,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't feel better, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:48.49,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You butt out, Luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:53.58,main,Shark mage,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to drag you into \Nmy dad's game like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:57.17,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Dad? You're that geezer's son?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:20:00.51,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,He's strong... His magic \Nis as deep as the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:04.82,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt about it... He's definitely \Nthe strongest one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:06.69,main,Shark mage,0000,0000,0000,,You two should come at me at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.69,0:20:10.02,main,Shark mage,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not hurt you \Nany more than I need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:12.77,main,Shark mage,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, I'll end \Nall this in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:16.23,main,Shark mage,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Sea God's Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:21.42,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You ain't ending anyone, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:24.14,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done having fun yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:33.52,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.52,0:20:34.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.87,0:20:37.92,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What the heck's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:50.35,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.63,0:20:56.39,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you let us join in?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:32.41,sign_33083_276_Petit_Clover_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,520)}Pe{\c&H3BC020&}t{\c&HE2AF0F&}i{\c&H3BC020&}t C{\c&HE2AF0F&}l{\c&H3BC020&}o{\c&H0E42D4&}ve{\c&H3BC020&}r
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.81,0:22:31.56,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.91,0:22:35.87,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Why Don't You Let Us Join In?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.79,0:22:35.87,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Why Don't You Let Us Join In?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.38,0:22:39.54,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.71,0:22:44.80,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you let us join in?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:46.42,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Munchy, munchy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.75,0:22:47.55,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.11,0:22:52.35,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I-I must've come to the wrong place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.73,0:22:56.10,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Munchy, munchy... Have a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.41,0:22:58.23,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Have a bite, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.14,0:23:07.11,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you insist, I guess I'll... join in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.93,0:23:09.92,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you join in...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.92,0:23:11.41,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,After you stir that pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.47,0:23:15.91,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Those who will not work do not get to munchy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.12,0:23:21.89,top,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Stir, stir, stir...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.97,0:23:21.89,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Put your back into it!\NIt's not all about strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.89,0:23:24.65,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I see... This is quite deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.27,0:23:31.06,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And so, Vetto realized his dream to become \Na chef and gave up on the magic stone.
